### Forecast - predict 7 days of food surplus
POST http://localhost:8080/api/forecast
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "historicalSurplus": [45.2, 50.1, 38.7, 60.0, 55.3, 42.1, 48.9, 52.3, 47.6, 61.2, 53.8, 44.5, 49.7, 58.1],
  "daysToPredict": 7
}

