### Route Optimisation - 3 locations, 2 vehicles
POST http://localhost:8080/api/optimize-route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locations": [
    {"name": "Food Bank Mumbai Central", "lat": 18.9690, "lng": 72.8205},
    {"name": "Restaurant Bandra",        "lat": 19.0596, "lng": 72.8295},
    {"name": "Shelter Dharavi",          "lat": 19.0176, "lng": 72.8562},
    {"name": "Cafe Andheri",             "lat": 19.1136, "lng": 72.8697},
    {"name": "NGO Colaba",               "lat": 18.9067, "lng": 72.8147}
  ],
  "vehicleCount": 2,
  "optimizationStrategy": "nearest_neighbour"
}